DTSTAMP:20260307T234439Z
DTSTART:20260314T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a day of pampering\, wellness\, fitness and shoppin
	g as we celebrate the importance of self-care!\n\n✨ Women’s Day Out: Sip\,
