	nt is open to all\, not just those who live in Washington! A participant c
	an only play a maximum of 4 events. 2 maximum of a specific type and no sk
	ipping flights.  We will have Mixed Doubles on Friday\, Singles on Saturda
	y and Doubles on Sunday and they will be played from start to end on the d
	ate Please email the Tournament Director \\(adrienne@seattlebadminton.com\
	\) if you have any questions! Sign-Up early and complete payment to secure
	 your spot! \\*A reminder that if you are playing doubles and/or mixed dou
	bles\, each player in a pair must sign up and pay in order to be eligible 
	to compete together.  We look forward to seeing you all! \\*Tournament ent
	ry fees cover snacks\, lunch\, t-shirts\, trophies\, and shuttles --------
